- ALTER TABLE user_updates ADD COLUMN room_id uuid REFERENCES rooms(id); -- nullable for now
- ALTER TABLE sessions ADD COLUMN room_id uuid REFERENCES rooms(id);

Idempotent. Verify: existing single-room cohort sees no UX change after migration.

